Class TConsole_TextOut

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IControllable

    public class TConsole_TextOut
extends VFrontend
implements IControllable
    A simple text-only frontend. Writes all peak values to stdout in csv format, one peak value per line. Line format: [chan_num],[peak_value] Where [chan_num] denotes the channel and [peak_value] denotes the value of the peak level. Channel numbers map as 0 (zero) for the left channel and 1 (one) for the right channel.
    Author:
    Peter Hoppe
